profile:
SPRING IS HERE ! BOOK YOUR SPOT BEFORE MAY 1st and get your HST waived on all products and services ! 

We Offer Top of the line work and products at a Reasonable and Affordable price. We Have Packages to Fit ANY Budget! 
Residential & Commercial! 

-Interior & Exterior Painting (Top of the line paints - Lifetime Warranty!) 
-Drywall Repairs 
-Deck & Fence Finishes 
-Wood Staining & Varnishing 
-Pressure Washing - Deck/Fence, Siding, Stone, Brick, You Name It!!! We will make it shine again! 

-Graffiti Removal 

Concrete Floor Epoxy - From base/clear, to a full out two tone metallic! - Make your floor a mind blowing show peice! 

-Driveway Sealing & Repairs (Using High Quality Epoxy Urethane Sealer) 5-10years Longevity Guaranteed! (vs 1year competition) 

What you can expect from us: 
Professional Work 
Top of the line paints/products at contractor pricing (Get a deal through us!!) 
Throughout Cleaning ( no messes guaranteed ! ) 
Knowledgeable, Friendly and Reliable Staff 
Licensed and Fully Insured! 

Bilingual Service , Servicing the Ottawa/Gatineau Area From East to West! 

Contact us today for your free estimate ! 

Visit our Website @ www.allpropaintingottawa.com 
or on Facebook @ www.facebook.com/allpropaintingandcoatings 

All Pro Painting co. 
613-222-6070
